5:[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"TVSeries\",\"name\":\"The Slime Diaries\",\"description\":\"“Dear diary… I got reincarnated as a slime.”<br>\\n<br>\\nEven in another world, lives aren’t always on the line. There’s plenty of work to be done, from feeding the community and forging the items the community needs; as well as plenty of play …and hijinks throughout! Join Rimuru and friends as they kick back and enjoy their daily lives.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Kodansha USA)\",\"image\":\"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx116741-MI9aI2ikNyAP.jpg\",\"datePublished\":\"2021-04-06\",\"numberOfEpisodes\":12,\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"inLanguage\":\"ja\",\"genre\":[\"Adventure\",\"Comedy\",\"Fantasy\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"aggregateRating\":{\"@type\":\"AggregateRating\",\"ratingValue\":7.4,\"bestRating\":10,\"ratingCount\":0}}"}}],["$","$L10",null,{"initialDrama":{"id":"00afffd3-c943-4bbe-a484-e84b506ddc5f","tmdb_id":116741,"imdb_id":null,"content_type":"anime","title":"The Slime Diaries","original_title":"転生したらスライムだった件 転スラ日記","overview":"“Dear diary… I got reincarnated as a slime.”<br>\n<br>\nEven in another world, lives aren’t always on the line. There’s plenty of work to be done, from feeding the community and forging the items the community needs; as well as plenty of play …and hijinks throughout! Join Rimuru and friends as they kick back and enjoy their daily lives.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Kodansha USA)","poster_path":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx116741-MI9aI2ikNyAP.jpg","backdrop_path":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/116741-PUZqZptAPjox.jpg","release_date":null,"first_air_date":"2021-04-06","status":"published","original_language":"ja","origin_country":["JP"],"genres":[{"id":1,"name":"Adventure"},{"id":2,"name":"Comedy"},{"id":3,"name":"Fantasy"},{"id":